## Quick Reference: Common Jenkinsfile Steps

```groovy
sh 'command'                          // run a shell command
bat 'command'                         // run a Windows batch command
echo 'message'                        // print to console log
checkout scm                          // check out the repo that triggered the build
git branch: 'main', url: 'https://github.com/user/repo.git'
archiveArtifacts artifacts: '**/*.jar'
junit '**/target/surefire-reports/*.xml'
stash name: 'jar', includes: 'target/*.jar'   // pass files between stages/agents
unstash 'jar'
input message: 'Deploy to production?'         // manual approval gate
timeout(time: 5, unit: 'MINUTES') { sh '...' }
retry(3) { sh '...' }
parallel(...)                                  // run stages/steps concurrently
```

