## Common CLI / Admin Tasks

```bash
# Jenkins CLI (via jenkins-cli.jar)
java -jar jenkins-cli.jar -s http://localhost:8080/ list-jobs
java -jar jenkins-cli.jar -s http://localhost:8080/ build my-job
java -jar jenkins-cli.jar -s http://localhost:8080/ console my-job

# Plugin management (Manage Jenkins → Plugins, or via CLI)
java -jar jenkins-cli.jar -s http://localhost:8080/ install-plugin docker-workflow

# Restart / safe-restart
java -jar jenkins-cli.jar -s http://localhost:8080/ safe-restart

# Backing up Jenkins (everything lives under JENKINS_HOME)
tar -czf jenkins-backup.tar.gz /var/jenkins_home
```

